tle=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of Monday \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/Monday\">Monday</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of month \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/month\">month</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of moon \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/moon\">moon</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of parameter \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/parameter\">parameter</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of pentameter \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/pentameter\">pentameter</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of perimeter \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/perimeter\">perimeter</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of piecemeal \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/piecemeal\">piecemeal</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of semester \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/semester\">semester</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of symmetry \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/symmetry\">symmetry</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of thermometer \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/thermometer\">thermometer</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of trigonometry \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/trigonometry\">trigonometry</a>; <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of trimester \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/trimester\">trimester</a>。</p><p>它是假设的来源/其存在的证据由以下提供：梵语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">mati</i> “测量”， <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">matra</i> “度量”； 阿维斯塔语，古波斯语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">ma-</i> “测量”； 希腊语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">metron</i> “测量”， <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">metra</i> “份额，部分”； 拉丁语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">metri</i> “测量”。</p>"
